<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="U" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Unbind" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Unbind,</orth> to untie, to loose: <cit><quote>now am I Dromio and his man unbound,</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 5.290" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. V, 290</bibl></cit> (or == not bound?). <cit><quote>u. my hands,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 2.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. II, 4</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>unbound the rest,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.201" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 201</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>u. my sons,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 3.1.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. III, 1, 24</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>